Nhevedzwa yemvura inotsanangudza mafambiro emvura pavhu, pasi pevhu uye mudenga riri pamusoro pevhu. Mvura inosanduka kubva pakuva magodo, mutuvi uye mwando panhambo dzakasiyana dzenhevedzwa dzemvura. Mvura inofamba munzvimbo dzakasiyana dzainoungana dzinoti: gungwa, nyanza, nzizi,mhepo. Izvi zvinoitika kuburikidza nezviitiko zvinoti: kunaya, kuyerera pavhu; kumimina nemuvhu; kusasauka ichienda mumhepo; kubundira mumakore; kuverereka kupinda mumhepo ichibva pamazaya echando; zvichingodaro. 

[[Rondedzero]]

Mvura iri mugungwa, nyanza, nenzizi ino[[sasauka]] kupinda mumhepo kuburukidza nekupisa kwezuva. Kunyika dzinotonhora, [[sinowo]], nemvura yakabundira nechando zvino[[verereka]] (sublimmation) kupinda mumhepo kuita [[mwando]]. Michero inodikitira mvura ichibuda mairi kupinda mumhepo. Kusumuka kwemweya unopisa kunosimudzawo [[mwando wemvura]] kuenda kumakore kunova kunotonhorera; kutonhora kuri mudenga kunokonzera kuti [[mwando wemvura]] ubundire uchigadzira makore. Mhepo iri mudenga inorakura mvura iya yabundira zvichiita kuti isangane nekunamana neimwe mvura yakabundira kuita makore. Imwe mvura iri mumakore inoturuka kuburikidza kunaya kwe[[sinowo]] kana chivhuramahwe; iyi mvura inokwanisa kuchengetwa kwemakore iri [[sinowo]] kana chando chakabundira munzvimbo dzinotonhora. Imwe [[sinowo]] inonyungudika mumwaka wekupisa. Mvura zhinji inonaya pamusoro pegungwa, uye padunhu apo inoyerera ichienda munzizi, nyanza, negungwa mainochengetedzwa. Chimwe chikamu chemvura inonaya padunhu inopinda muvhu mainochenetedzwa tichizoinwa kubva mumatsime nezvibhorani. Imwe yemvura yepasi iyi inomimina ichinopinda pakaungana mvura munzizi, nyanza, negungwa; imwe mvura inotubuka ichibuda muvhu se[[chisipiti]]


